<p>First things first: make sure your Mac&#039;s XProtect database is regularly updated. With that out of the way, we can have some fun learning some handy new keyboard shortcuts, new ways to filter Mail on your iPhone and iPad, some tricks for truly securing your router, and a discussion about guest networks, just to name a few topics included in this week&#039;s episode. Press play, and enjoy learning at least five new things!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
